"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?0/63/1012/abstract/4\">",
"      Chow WH, McLaughlin JK, Linet MS, et al. Use of analgesics and risk of renal cell cancer. Int J Cancer 1994; 59:467.",
"     </a>",
